response.overview: "Decade of Dominance" relives one of the most exceptional eras in SEC football, with behind-the-scenes moments, mic'd up sound and interviews with those who played pivotal roles in the greatness. Viewers will hear from Heisman Trophy winners Derrick Henry, Joe Burrow and DeVonta Smith, as well as Patrick Queen, Justin Jefferson, Kirby Smart, Nakobe Dean, Jordan Davis, Mac Jones, Brock Bowers and Ladd McConkey as they watch their past selves compete on college football's biggest stage.â€”SEC Network
response.title: Decade of Dominance
